snippet.title: Biffa Plays Indie Games
snippet.description:
Unwind with a cuppa Tea as we build, survive and create together. Hi my name is Biffa! I love to play Indie Games including Sandbox, Survival, City/Base Builders & Strategy style games like Surviving Mars, Cities Skylines, Oxygen Not Included, Planet Coaster & MORE!! Tea is my beverage of choice with English Breakfast Tea being the best!! ;-)

►How to SUPPORT Me:
- My Patreon if you wish to support me:
  http://www.patreon.com/Biffa2001

►Where to FOLLOW Me:
- Indie Games: https://www.youtube.com/c/BiffaPlaysIndie
- Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/biffa2001
- Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/biffa2001

►Current PC Spec
Fractal Design Define R5 Titanium Mid ATX 
AMD Ryzen 9 3900X
64GB Corsair Vengeance RGB PRO DDR4 3466mhz
Gigabyte RTX 2080TI 11GB
3 x LG 27UL650 27" 4K UHD Monitors

My Email is for BUSINESS use only. Do not email me Cities to fix or junctions you've made! THEY WILL BE DELETED. See the pinned post on my videos for info on how to send them to me. Thanks :-)
